refrain from partnering and having linkage with unregistered and unauthorized NGO; 



instruct the Municipal Treasurer to issue Official Receipt or electronic receipt for all cash donations received by the LGU or its alter ego and issue Acknowledgment Receipt for all in-kind aids/donations received for proper accountability;

instruct the Inventory Committee to conduct inventory, revaluation and recording in the books of account all undistributed items from in-kind donations, if there’s any;
direct the Municipal Accountant to scrutinize the strict adherence to the proper supporting documentation of every disbursement under COA Circular No. 2012-001 dated June 14, 2012 and comply with the reporting guidelines of cash donations and in-kind donations; and 

advise the LDRRMO to copy furnished the Audit Team of the report submitted to the NDRRMC through the Office of Civil Defense (OCD).

