instruct the OIC-HRMO to (i) submit the DTRs or any other means of recording attendance; Order authorizing the employees to physically report for work; and duly validated Accomplishment Reports of the concerned officials and employees, and submit the same to the Municipal Accountant to validate all the payments made; 

